{"tid":1712582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全民巴士死火師","createTime":"2019-11-12T14:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T15:59:11.000Z","uid":24753,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"995d0997e81424d10007c6e54fe8ec9526d55f18","tid":1712582,"uid":24753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"處於巴士站既手足，唔好做以下既事：<br />\n1.扮等車<br />\n2.用紙巾包一包手指<br />\n3.係人上緊車既時侯搵出緊急死火掣（多數係車尾），㩒一㩒<br />\n4.離開<br />\n<br />\n咁樣做車長要重新啟動引擎，可以浪費唔少時間<br />\n經過今日中大一戰，希望大家都幫幫手，用諗到既辦法去抗爭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於緊急死火掣位置<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kJLNbZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1kJLNbZ.jpg&h=ba5bd161&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZgJyR0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZgJyR0.jpg&h=640809fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7G9yV5n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7G9yV5n.jpg&h=42796ca7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtCdbDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtCdbDK.jpg&h=b835827e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/12/224723_4decdd211619308d8d6dc36b0579a63f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F12%2F224723_4decdd211619308d8d6dc36b0579a63f.jpg&h=a5f2c139&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/upjbHLs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FupjbHLs.jpg&h=dc4f9fd0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWB9uqt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWB9uqt.jpg&h=e214f24d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://hkbus.fandom.com/wiki/%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%AD%BB%E7%81%AB%E6%8E%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkbus.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E7%2581%25AB%25E6%258E%25A3&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7W58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=6e3cff74\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkbus.fandom.com/wiki/%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%AD%BB%E7%81%AB%E6%8E%A3</a>"},{"pid":"85c5dfaba97e54fe7b9b1bcfa1bfca24dd883f97","tid":1712582,"uid":273825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:49:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好咁做</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fefdad6ba67a2066eca5a395762e58fa4df8c46","tid":1712582,"uid":24753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"90a03fbbf39047cae4292334be0a533b72f7f4b0","tid":1712582,"uid":24753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0fc1978a126111837d2a67ee87bd035dc33912c3","tid":1712582,"uid":24753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e932bbae1c0c35295d19f8c0ca91574a61b36a0a","tid":1712582,"uid":24753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:51:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8decd204e961334498070cfb11d482e2e1d49e9c","tid":1712582,"uid":217897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"825a35f348ef8e01957449ab3e7a016f311a4b56","tid":1712582,"uid":24753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8a42a216b999470cb469d3d548c72f4cdbc1270f","tid":1712582,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"唔好啦"},{"pid":"e185a14b8b3de6a7353b057b8087609fa97f0b08","tid":1712582,"uid":24753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:52:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"186b3d3dc24ecabf4a84aaa29223f4234ee3f2cb","tid":1712582,"uid":24753,"like":0,"dislike":0,